long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
FaceSwap provides free face swapping service for photos and videos. It allows you enjoy unlimited swaps without any payment. This face swapper includes the following key features:

AI Face Swapping Technology: Using advanced AI to recognize facial features and seamlessly morph two faces, resulting in realistic swapped photos and videos.

Quick Photo Faceswap: Swap faces on any photo in just seconds and get high-resolution results for single or group photos.

High Quality Video Faceswap: Easily swap faces in videos to create entertaining clips. Whether you’re looking for a fun twist to your home videos or create viral content for social media, this face swapping service delivers realistic results. 

Easy to Use: with this face swapper, completing the swapping process is as easy as two simple steps. No complicated operations, just select the photo or video you want to swap, upload it, and you’re done!

100% Free: FaceSwap plugin is a completely free extension that lets you enjoy unlimited face swaps in both photos and videos. Unlike other face swapper which only offers limited free trials, FaceSwap gives you endless possibilities everyday. 

Customized Swapping: tailor your face swaps to perfection with customization options. Adjust and refine each swap to create the exact look you want. 

Privacy Protection: we ensures that your photos and videos remain private and secure. We use advanced encryption and never store your data, so you can swap faces with complete peace of mind.
